Abbreviations in alphabetical order: +, positive for melanoma metastases; -, negative for melanoma metastases; cn, capsular nevus; FR, final result;
                     IC, rapid intraoperative immunocytochemistry; Intm, indeterminate for melanoma metastases; LN, sentinel and non-sentinel lymph nodes; N, negative; P,
                     positive; SP, final result on permanent sections.
